trans-unit.source: Represents an extensibility element added to an <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.InputBinding"></xref> or an <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OutputBinding"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 表示可扩展性元素添加到<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.InputBinding"></xref>或<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OutputBinding"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新实例<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding"></xref>类。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a string containing a list of space-delimited URIs.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置一个包含用空格分隔的 Uri 列表的字符串。

trans-unit.source: The URIs represent the encoding style (or styles) to be used to encode messages within the SOAP body.
trans-unit.target: Uri 表示的编码样式 （或样式） 要用于对 SOAP 正文中的消息进行编码。

trans-unit.source: The value of this property should be set only if the value of the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Use%2A> property is `Encoded`.
trans-unit.target: 才应设置此属性的值的值<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Use%2A>属性是`Encoded`。</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Use%2A>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise this property value will be ignored.
trans-unit.target: 否则将忽略此属性的值。

trans-unit.source: A string containing a list of URIs.
trans-unit.target: 包含的 Uri 列表的字符串。

trans-unit.source: The default value is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: 默认值为空字符串 ("")。

trans-unit.source: Get or sets the URI representing the location of the specifications for encoding of content not specifically defined by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Encoding*> property.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置表示的不是专门定义的内容编码的规范的位置的 URI<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Encoding*>属性。</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Encoding*>

trans-unit.source: This property will return an empty string ("") if the property value has not been set.
trans-unit.target: 此属性将返回空字符串 ("") 如果尚未设置的属性值。

trans-unit.source: The value should only be set if the value of the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Use%2A> property is `Encoded`.
trans-unit.target: 如果应仅设置的值的值<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Use%2A>属性是`Encoded`。</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Use%2A>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise the property value will be ignored, thus leading to unexpected behavior by the XML Web service.
trans-unit.target: 否则属性值将被忽略，因此导致意外行为，由 XML Web 服务。

trans-unit.source: A string containing a URI.
trans-unit.target: 包含 URI 的字符串。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating which parts of the transmitted message appear within the SOAP body portion of the transmission.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置一个值，该值指示在传输的 SOAP 正文部分内显示传输的消息中的哪些部分。

trans-unit.source: Some parts of the transmitted message can appear in portions other than the SOAP body, such as when SOAP is used with a <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding>.
trans-unit.target: 传输的消息的某些部分可以出现在 SOAP 主体，例如，当 SOAP <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding>。</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding>以外的某些部分

trans-unit.source: In such a case, the other members of the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart.Extensions%2A> property determine the locations of the other parts of the message.
trans-unit.target: 在这种情况下的其他成员<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart.Extensions%2A>属性确定消息的其他部分的位置。</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart.Extensions%2A>

trans-unit.source: This property returns exactly the same information as the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.PartsString%2A> property, but the results are returned within an array rather than within a space-delimited string.
trans-unit.target: 此属性返回与相同的信息<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.PartsString%2A>属性，但结果返回数组中而不是用空格分隔的字符串内。</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.PartsString%2A>

trans-unit.source: A string array containing the names of the appropriate message parts.
trans-unit.target: 包含适当的消息部分的名称的字符串数组。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating which parts of the transmitted message appear within the SOAP body portion of the transmission.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置一个值，该值指示在传输的 SOAP 正文部分内显示传输的消息中的哪些部分。

trans-unit.source: Some parts of the transmitted message can appear in portions other than the SOAP body, such as when SOAP is used with a <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding>.
trans-unit.target: 传输的消息的某些部分可以出现在 SOAP 主体，例如，当 SOAP <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding>。</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding>以外的某些部分

trans-unit.source: In such a case, the other members of the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart.Extensions%2A> property determine the locations of other parts of the message.
trans-unit.target: 在这种情况下的其他成员<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart.Extensions%2A>属性确定消息的其他部分的位置。</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart.Extensions%2A>

trans-unit.source: This property returns exactly the same information as the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Parts%2A> property, but the results are returned within a space-delimited string rather than within an array.
trans-unit.target: 此属性返回与相同的信息<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Parts%2A>属性，但结果返回用空格分隔的字符串内而不是数组中。</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Parts%2A>

trans-unit.source: PartsString is used internally for xml serialization and shouldn't be called directly.
trans-unit.target: PartsString 可供内部用于 xml 序列化，而且不应直接调用。

trans-unit.source: To return the transmitted message parts appearing within the SOAP body portion of the transmission, use the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Parts%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 若要返回传输的 SOAP 正文部分内出现的传输的消息部分，使用<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Parts%2A>属性。</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Parts%2A>

trans-unit.source: A space-delimited string containing the appropriate message parts.
trans-unit.target: 包含适当的消息部分用空格分隔的字符串。

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether the message parts are encoded using specified encoding rules, or define the concrete schema of the message.
trans-unit.target: 指示消息部分进行编码，使用指定的编码规则还是定义消息的具体架构。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Namespace%2A> and <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Encoding%2A> properties depend on the value of this property.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Namespace%2A>和<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Encoding%2A>属性依赖于此属性的值。</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Encoding%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding.Namespace%2A>

trans-unit.source: Their values should be set only if the value of this property is `Encoded`.
trans-unit.target: 此属性的值时才应设置其值`Encoded`。

trans-unit.source: Otherwise the XML Web service will produce unexpected behavior.
trans-unit.target: 否则 XML Web 服务将产生意外的行为。

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBindingUse"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: 之一<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBindingUse"></xref>值。

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_Default" name="Default" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 默认值是<xref uid="langword_csharp_Default" name="Default" href=""> </xref>。
